DPM_TEAM04_Package

Class Resources

  • java.lang.Object
    • DPM_TEAM04_Package.Resources

  • public class Resources
extends java.lang.Object
    This class contains all resources (Motors, Sensors, Filters, Display) and all constants required for operation. Resources are initialized once this class is loaded by the JVM Sensor data is also acquired through this class
    Version:
    2.0
    Author:
    Kareem Halabi
